{"tid":7130,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位巴絲諗諗","createTime":"2016-11-27T17:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T17:55:35.000Z","uid":17224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d2c343855d0720a21cfa10288c40231ffc8de15b","tid":7130,"uid":17224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:00:32.000Z","msg":"喺呢度生活咗咁耐 <br />\n以前啲人點都仲會有啲笑容 一份熱情<br />\n但係而家就.... <br />\n我好希望大家平時表情唔好咁麻木<br />\n我明白返工返學 好辛苦....<br />\n但係喺平日喺社會 <br />\n甚至喺街上<br />\n多一份溫暖嘅笑容 熱情<br />\n試下觀察平日身邊嘅人同事<br />\n有冇咩可以幫到手<br />\n減少社會嘅戾氣<br />\n少啲紛爭<br />\n唔係更好咩<br />\nSor 好似有啲左膠<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然...遇到唔社會公平嘅事 <br />\n或者比啲仆街大陸佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n寸步不讓 <br />\n努力爭取<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n放鬆啲啦 香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 林早逝 我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPs 聽日仲要返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b26a6808ed17440f579314bd256d5b2f32a652","tid":7130,"uid":9520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c181f06db57685a925a2cff915a2b2e37ab1ba06","tid":7130,"uid":776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:08:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aacf4cb7b097ba6202c94c503467f51da2a572dd","tid":7130,"uid":17224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gi